Tabera de Abajo

Tabera de Abajo is a city in Salamanca, in Spain.

GPS Coordinates of Tabera de Abajo, Salamanca, Spain

Tabera de Abajo is located on the latitude of 40.91021 and longitude of -6.00227 and has a geohash of ez78xrmr0zzh.

Cities and Towns near Tabera de Abajo

The nearest significant population center from Tabera de Abajo is Canillas de Abajo in Salamanca, Spain, located 6 kilometers or 3 miles ↗ NE of the city. Other locations in close proximity include Aldehuela de la Bóveda (Salamanca, Spain) located 7 km (4 mi) ↓ S and Calzada de Don Diego (Salamanca, Spain) located 8 km (5 mi) → E of Tabera de Abajo.

In total, we found 50 cities near Tabera de Abajo in our database.
